summary:
New Dungeon (Odin\'s Tomb) and armor reward at the end 
http://youtu.be/WCr2gNBA9Fo
descriptionHtml:
Odin\'s Tomb will be episode 1 of a series of mods, episode 1 contains the first part of an armor set and each following mod will contain another piece of armor, the armor will be heavy armor and you will be required to fight through a series of dungeons to receive the armor.

Youtube series on the making of : http://youtu.be/WCr2gNBA9Fo
